Course Search

Search Criteria

 
 
 
Field of Education:  
 
 
 
     
     
 
     
 
  OR:

Search Examples:

  • To search for all Bachelor of Economics Degree courses offered in New South Wales:
    • Click on the Reset button to reset the form;
    • Select Education from the Field of Education - Broad Field drop down list box;
    • Select Bachelor Degree from the Type of Course drop down list box;
    • Select New South Wales from the State drop down list box; and
    • Click on the Start Search button to commence the search.

  • To search for all courses that have the word hospitality in their title:
    • Click on the Reset button to reset the form;
    • Type: hospitality in the Course Name text box; and
    • Click on the Start Search button to commence the search.

  • To display details of the course with a CRICOS course code of 022217A:
    • Click on the Reset button to reset the form;
    • Type: 022217A in the Course Code text box; and
    • Click on the Start Search button to commence the search.
